title: Ventev Powercell 6000+ Portable Battery Charger 532972 - Overview
description:
Ventev Powercell 6000+ Portable Battery Charger - 532972
http://www.abt.com/product/96988/Ventev-532972.html

A 6000mAh backup battery that delivers 25 hours to your mobile device so you are never without power. Dual USB ports 1A ideal for handsets and a 2.1A rapid charging port perfect for tablets.
Features:
• Charging port perfect for tablets
• Charges handsets tablets and other USB devices; 2.1A port will charge your device at its max rate
• Capacity to charge any two devices at once
• Short circuit and temperature protection
